ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>要用電<br />\n發電要能源，會排放溫室氣體</blockquote><br />\n咁相對家用冷氣機<br />\n工業用 商業用既機器先係主要耗電<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7af33aa74b322a92fd848288083179a78a64327","tid":791408,"uid":137233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"將能量抽出都要能量"},{"pid":"e8ce2915f600b27d90cfdbe512f450d73c33cd70","tid":791408,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"騙局黎，我開親間房都好凍，邊有暖"},{"pid":"55bf7e89a5166a7d137384186d3b9189232723c1","tid":791408,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7af33aa74b322a92fd848288083179a78a64327","tid":791408,"uid":137233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"將能量抽出都要能量"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:26:19.000Z","msg":"可以查下entropy(熵)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a574ec104d308609c2f55d6942e02716ff05b832","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T19:43:36.000Z","msg":"打個比喻 <br />\n冷氣就係個水桶 講室內啲熱能裝滿後倒出室內 咁倒個過程都要energy 先得"},{"pid":"99efd59dffbf3f98246364894d6f45e11b1387e2","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"13fa33b8317e46de61d07f6c56da16cfe4a089e5","tid":791408,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"明明只係將室內熱能抽出 但overall 空氣既熱能不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:04:54.000Z","msg":"#5 #7 正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2nd law of thermodynamics 裡面有句 Clausius statement (或者叫 &quot;refrigerator statement&quot;)<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>&quot;It is impossible for any process to have as its sole result the transfer of heat from a cooler to a hotter body.&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亦都即係話由一個溫度較低嘅物件轉移熱能去溫度較高嘅物件一定需要做功 (work)，呢 D 功會以 waste heat 嘅形式排放出外部環境。<br />\n<br />\n不過冷氣令全球暖化嘅論調最主要來源唔係呢個，而係冷氣以前用嘅雪種係 Chlorofluorocarbons (CFCs)，呢隻雪種會造成臭氧層空洞，令臭氧層無辦法吸收短波紫外線，呢個先係最主要全球暖化嘅元兇。不過而家 CFCs 嘅雪種已經被淘汰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7efb314944deca2da614c4cea62f4fe56bb47ca","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:08:24.000Z","msg":"戰鬥力不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一時間諗唔到點解釋樓主個 situation 同 entropy 嘅關係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他巴打接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},{"pid":"5668bd92a7fa97cc1f31dff1bf711ba5381be304","tid":791408,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:11:46.000Z","msg":"連登科學家全面進場"},{"pid":"bafb010a495f13d1a561d69feacfa8f02cfab1c3","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:20:02.000Z","msg":"大部分冷氣機製冷&gt;所需熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCoefficient_of_performance&d=Y6b7QeYkFTja28voM7JRQPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=602073c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance</a>"},{"pid":"0cd6a8c1ca8236085e49f261425b92469bcf02ee","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:21:19.000Z","msg":"應該攞得諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時改寫 1st law 同 2nd law of thermodynamics<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8a349fff1a16f7b8bfa8e9788fb7153b8a3006","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafb010a495f13d1a561d69feacfa8f02cfab1c3","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:20:02.000Z","msg":"大部分冷氣機製冷&gt;所需熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCoefficient_of_performance&d=Y6b7QeYkFTja28voM7JRQPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=602073c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:24:16.000Z","msg":"表示唔識睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6048bb803d16aebd11fb1d97280479d7826ae63f","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafb010a495f13d1a561d69feacfa8f02cfab1c3","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:20:02.000Z","msg":"大部分冷氣機製冷&gt;所需熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCoefficient_of_performance&d=Y6b7QeYkFTja28voM7JRQPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=602073c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:28:16.000Z","msg":"咦我理解錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQc 係製冷，但係 dump 出去嘅熱能應該係 Qh + W<br />\n定係佢講嘅所需<del>熱</del>功剩係講 W？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfffc68c94bb9b679a4b43ac820fce70b78a4bfa","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T21:17:18.000Z","msg":"我嘗試一下解釋冷氣運作同 entropy 嘅關係先。<br />\n<br />\nEntropy S 係一個 thermodynamic variable，代表緊一個 thermodynamic system 嘅狀態 (state)。用直觀嘅角度entropy 代表住一個 system 嘅&quot;無序&quot; (disorder/randomness)，個 system 愈係無序，entropy 就愈大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/044532_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F044532_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=5ae76727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如上圖入面，<br />\n下面嘅 tube 比上面嘅有更多嘅 entropy<br />\n而由上面嘅 tube 演變成下面嘅過程我哋叫佢做 free expansion<br />\n可以想像下原本上面嘅 tube 原本有幅 partition 隔住，氣體嘅粒子只係喺個 partition 嘅左面<br />\n突然有一刻有個人拎起塊 partition ，粒子就以類似 diffusion 嘅形式擴散到成條管，entropy 因此而增加<br />\n呢個 process 係 irreversible 嘅，喺冇主觀意志下唔會話 D 粒子自己走返晒去左邊<br />\n就好似你將一包糖同一包鹽混埋一起，分返開係冇可能嘅<br />\n<br />\n詳細原因 statistical mechanics 有得解釋：<br />\n大自然會傾向移向一個存在機率更高嘅狀態<br />\n例如喺下面嘅 system<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/24/045708_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F24%2F045708_c7da2202001ef3739c67954b4c9dbb31.PNG&h=e0f582cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIII 明顯存在機率最高，所以大自然偏向會於流向 III 呢個 entropy 最高嘅狀態<br />\n呢個就係 2nd law of thermodynamics 嘅基礎：<br />\n宇宙嘅 entropy S 會傾向上升，唔會下降 i.e. &Delta;S &ge; 0<br />\n<br />\n咁 entropy 同 thermodynamics 有咩關係呢？<br />\n喺 classical thermodynamics 入面<br />\nEntropy S = &int;dQ / T<br />\nQ 係熱能嘅轉變<br />\nT 係該系統嘅溫度<br />\n<br />\n為咗方便解釋，我扔走所有 calculus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAssume 一個慢嘅 isothermal process，<br />\n&Delta;S = Q / T （經簡化嘅 definition）<br />\n小學雞時代話熱能由較熱嘅物體流向較冷嘅物體<br />\n其實係源自 2nd law of thermodynamics<br />\n<br />\n假設有物件 a 同物件 b 接觸，熱能由 a 流向 b，a 嘅溫度係 Ta，b 嘅溫度係 Tb。<br />\nTotal &Delta;S = -Q / Ta + Q / Tb = Q(1/Tb - 1/Ta)<br />\n<br />\n當 Ta &gt; Tb，&Delta;S 就 &gt;0。呢個就係正常熱由熱嘅物件流向冷物件嘅情況。<br />\n但係當 Tb &gt; Ta，&Delta;S 就 &lt;0。呢個係違反咗 2nd law of thermodynamics，係唔存在嘅情形。<br />\n呢個正正吻合咗上面 po 我講嘅 refrigerator statement，<br />\n所以 &Delta;S &ge; 0 同上面嘅 refrigerator statement 其實係相通嘅。<br />\n<br />\n一個冷氣要將 Q 由較冷嘅 b 扔去較熱嘅 a，同時又唔可以違反 &Delta;S &ge; 0 呢個定律，就必須額外提供能量 / 功 (Work W)，而呢個 W 嘅能量最後會同 Q 一併扔去較熱嘅 a。<br />\n呢個 W 就解釋咗冇冷氣可以做到 100% efficient，<br />\n亦都即係話樓主所講熱能 overall 相等呢句嘢唔正確。<br />\n<br />\n先 po 住咁多先。<br />\n詳細解釋需要牽涉到 Carnot engine 同埋 engine efficiency 等等嘅嘢，極度複雜。<br />\n我而家完全係戰鬥力不足解釋唔到咁多住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93f0db5292e08d132d24106d1bbb82dd7cd0139","tid":791408,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"47fc8feda38dbb1708a828af7f76ba2a73515e0e","tid":791408,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"微型核能冷氣機有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac14382bf23ddb4359ab2af370a816c49db4120","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6048bb803d16aebd11fb1d97280479d7826ae63f","tid":791408,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bafb010a495f13d1a561d69feacfa8f02cfab1c3","tid":791408,"uid":155943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dda41f8cc93f0b70b3effe8bb6273a11138028a9","tid":791408,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:10:23.000Z","msg":"其實而家只要發明到一樣<br />\n製冷&gt;所需熱能既機器<br />\n個個人應該會發達??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:20:02.000Z","msg":"大部分冷氣機製冷&gt;所需熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCoefficient_of_performance&d=Y6b7QeYkFTja28voM7JRQPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=602073c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coefficient_of_performance</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T20:28:16.000Z","msg":"咦我理解錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQc 係製冷，但係 dump 出去嘅熱能應該係 Qh + W<br />\n定係佢講嘅所需<del>熱</del>功剩係講 W？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"Qc=Qh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e810457cff74dc51d5aa88c8f92af12dab3fa5","tid":791408,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f4dea06720132c418ad2ec9df4d8c6bd6ec885","tid":791408,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47fc8feda38dbb1708a828af7f76ba2a73515e0e","tid":791408,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"微型核能冷氣機有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T01:53:08.000Z","msg":"應該係要核融合發電廠<br />\n其實電係一種乾淨能源<br />\n之不過發電過程會污染環境"},{"pid":"0311f085dc14f1c7b3374f314d8c8b873bc52b9a","tid":791408,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"區域冷氣系統"}]}